The paper deals with instance segmentation, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed solution involves the use of deep convolutional neural networks (cs.LG) and mathematical representations (cs.AI) to solve the problem. The paper also discusses reducing computational costs (cs.NE) and classification of image objects (cs.CL).
